{"tid":1974830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒：特朗普應承認台灣國家地位，否認「一中」","createTime":"2020-04-16T06:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:04:48.000Z","uid":278587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"684b4cae41d1a98c8923bb5fda020b443dd19754","tid":1974830,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/p476x249/93018692_236206607582661_6849575936279445504_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=eaa83b&amp;_nc_ohc=xDAIttqrikAAX8009ao&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=be2b101861c16ba710287756d4eb3e9f&amp;oe=5EBDC0AB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fp476x249%2F93018692_236206607582661_6849575936279445504_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3Deaa83b%26_nc_ohc%3DxDAIttqrikAAX8009ao%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Dbe2b101861c16ba710287756d4eb3e9f%26oe%3D5EBDC0AB&h=e98d0036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政論雜誌《國家評論》（National Review）周二（14日）刊登文章，指「是時候糾正台灣在國際舞台上的屈辱待遇」，文章從去年的NBA禁播事件，細數到武漢肺炎全球大流行，展示出中國如何威脅全球組織，及發揮地緣政治的力量，打壓香港抗爭者，並文化滅絕新疆維吾爾族人。文章呼籲美國總統特朗普承認台灣的國家地位，並消除虛構的「一中政策」。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，台灣是蔣介石國共內戰失敗後逃往的小島，如今已成為民主、自由和人類繁榮的典範，享有廣泛的言論自由，不會因宗教信仰遭受迫害，而且擁有自己獨特的文化，不受中國政府約束，即是說台灣不屬於「中華人民共和國」，承認台灣是一個自由且獨立的國家，也是一個道德倫理上的決定。<br />\n<br />\n文章強調，美國不該讓世界取信於中國所形容的中國，應向世界其他地區發出訊號，並向中國表明，台灣是一個獨立的國家，且是威權統治遭受苦難者的希望燈塔，「如果地球最強大國家的領導人不敢對中國說真話，那就沒有人會講。」<br />\n<br />\n文章以美國前總統列根推倒德國柏林圍牆為例，呼籲特朗普對中國說「夠了」，並激勵其他敢於反抗中國威權的人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200416/MBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200416%2FMBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2d2aefec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200416%2FMBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU%2F&h=b9ca3edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200416/MBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU/</a>"},{"pid":"c8d0a984de3b5d45e355e50c5faa3dcbd9754b9c","tid":1974830,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"684b4cae41d1a98c8923bb5fda020b443dd19754","tid":1974830,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/p476x249/93018692_236206607582661_6849575936279445504_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=eaa83b&amp;_nc_ohc=xDAIttqrikAAX8009ao&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=be2b101861c16ba710287756d4eb3e9f&amp;oe=5EBDC0AB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fp476x249%2F93018692_236206607582661_6849575936279445504_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3Deaa83b%26_nc_ohc%3DxDAIttqrikAAX8009ao%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Dbe2b101861c16ba710287756d4eb3e9f%26oe%3D5EBDC0AB&h=e98d0036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政論雜誌《國家評論》（National Review）周二（14日）刊登文章，指「是時候糾正台灣在國際舞台上的屈辱待遇」，文章從去年的NBA禁播事件，細數到武漢肺炎全球大流行，展示出中國如何威脅全球組織，及發揮地緣政治的力量，打壓香港抗爭者，並文化滅絕新疆維吾爾族人。文章呼籲美國總統特朗普承認台灣的國家地位，並消除虛構的「一中政策」。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，台灣是蔣介石國共內戰失敗後逃往的小島，如今已成為民主、自由和人類繁榮的典範，享有廣泛的言論自由，不會因宗教信仰遭受迫害，而且擁有自己獨特的文化，不受中國政府約束，即是說台灣不屬於「中華人民共和國」，承認台灣是一個自由且獨立的國家，也是一個道德倫理上的決定。<br />\n<br />\n文章強調，美國不該讓世界取信於中國所形容的中國，應向世界其他地區發出訊號，並向中國表明，台灣是一個獨立的國家，且是威權統治遭受苦難者的希望燈塔，「如果地球最強大國家的領導人不敢對中國說真話，那就沒有人會講。」<br />\n<br />\n文章以美國前總統列根推倒德國柏林圍牆為例，呼籲特朗普對中國說「夠了」，並激勵其他敢於反抗中國威權的人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200416/MBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200416%2FMBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2d2aefec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200416%2FMBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU%2F&h=b9ca3edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200416/MBWDVORIWPQ7FPWRBNM5NGDGOU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"It&rsquo;s Time to Rectify Taiwan&rsquo;s Shameful Treatment on the International Stage<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nationalreview.com/2020/04/its-time-to-rectify-taiwans-shameful-treatment-on-the-international-stage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fits-time-to-rectify-taiwans-shameful-treatment-on-the-international-stage%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2906d3a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nationalreview.com/2020/04/its-time-to-rectify-taiwans-shameful-treatment-on-the-international-stage/</a>"},{"pid":"e488268d988a76a09a2235ea6a2d10ccc8927162","tid":1974830,"uid":227813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣是香港第十九管轄小島！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aadcf98f9084c003324143a9c8c2c89bbb43f0d","tid":1974830,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e488268d988a76a09a2235ea6a2d10ccc8927162","tid":1974830,"uid":227813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣是香港第十九管轄小島！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa